parameters.name: MOM_DENS
parameters.description: Column contains ion moment density in units of ions/cm**3.

parameters.name: MOM_VR
parameters.description:
Column contains ion moment velocity radial component (RTN coordinates,
                        Sun-spacecraft direction) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: MOM_VT
parameters.description:
Column contains ion moment velocity North/South component (RTN
                        coordinates, positive northward) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: MOM_VN
parameters.description:
Column contains ion moment velocity azimuthal component (RTN coordinates,
                        positive in the direction of planetary motion) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: MOM_V
parameters.description: Column contains ion moment velocity magnitude in units of km/s.

parameters.name: MOM_WTH
parameters.description: Column contains ion moment thermal speed in units of km/s.

parameters.name: FIT_DENS
parameters.description: Column contains ion fit density in units of ions/cm**3

parameters.name: FIT_VR
parameters.description:
Column contains ion fit velocity radial component (RTN coordinates,
                        Sun-spacecraft direction) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: FIT_VT
parameters.description:
Column contains ion fit velocity North/South component (RTN coordinates,
                        positive northward) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: FIT_VN
parameters.description:
Column contains ion fit velocity azimuthal component (RTN coordinates,
                        positive in the direction of planetary motion) in units of km/s.

parameters.name: FIT_V
parameters.description: Column contains ion fit velocity magnitude in units of km/s.

parameters.name: FIT_WTH
parameters.description: Column contains ion fit thermal speed in units of km/s
